rules.name: myRule_9
rules.label: Origin Equals Email, FaceBook, Twitter and Messanger

value.stringValue: AND ( ISNEW(), OR(ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'Facebook'),ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'Twitter'),ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'Facebook Messenger'), AND(OR(ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'Email'), ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'Sales Information'), ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'SASSI Internal'), ISPICKVAL([Case].Origin, 'System & Tariff')), [Case].CreatedBy.LastName = 'SAS Automation Process' ) ) )

formulas.name: formula_myRule_9
formulas.expression: AND ( ISNEW(), OR(ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'Facebook'),ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'Twitter'),ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'Facebook Messenger'), AND(OR(ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'Email'), ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'Sales Information'), ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'SASSI Internal'), ISPICKVAL({!myVariable_current.Origin}, 'System & Tariff')), {!myVariable_current.CreatedBy.LastName} = 'SAS Automation Process' ) ) )
